{"tid":1487253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 文宣要加樣好重要嘅野！","createTime":"2019-08-19T07:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:42:26.000Z","uid":174386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5922abba50b0db31ac1f7a4b15b1f72c0404ef8e","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"琴日睇到立場 王尚一 一篇嘅政治文<br />\n發現大家都忽略咗 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經濟</span> 哩一個點！<br />\n其實影響經濟嘅唔係示威者！<br />\n 以下係我high light 咗嘅重點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQfNKMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQfNKMa.jpg&h=d30c550a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1Bk4Mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1Bk4Mb.jpg&h=a4e2a15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中美貿易戰其實已經拖垮香港經濟<br />\n再加上中共一直掏空香港人嘅財富</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyaNKM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyaNKM5.png&h=2c033f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEpe9dM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEpe9dM.png&h=beeb5e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結！！！</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">話俾全港人知道，林鄭賣港，一直幫中共掏空香港人哩幾十年嚟累積嘅財富！ 然後中美貿易戰，中國更拖垮香港經濟！中國因中美貿易戰亦急於把香港的財富抽乾。香港亦就快被掏光！</span><br />\n即使冇反送中運動，香港遲早一日會被抽乾財富，而在中地位亦一直下降，終有一天會變成深圳市香港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，亦都從頭到尾都唔係示威者影響經濟!!班港豬廢中廢老亦最睇重經濟。拎住哩樣做文宣，日後如果再想搞三罷，可以發揮有效的宣傳效果！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲可以研究一下立場 王尚一 哩篇嘅政治文(有d長)但花時間睇完會有所啟發<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/中共滅亡之香港篇-一/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%BB%85%E4%BA%A1%E4%B9%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AF%87-%E4%B8%80%2F&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF469qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=b1b2c8e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%BB%85%E4%BA%A1%E4%B9%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AF%87-%E4%B8%80%2F&h=a217a6d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/中共滅亡之香港篇-一/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">香港人加油呀！<br />\n我地一定要贏！<br />\n要救返700多位手足出嚟！<br />\n輸咗只能成為歷史！<br />\n贏咗就能成為傳奇！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"79403d7f8b77839a80f84e59b7c817f2796da42c","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f124b01d53f81c8e1b7837f41489a2cc8dca9dc6","tid":1487253,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投資國難五金發國難財Ver 2.0</span></span><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"1a52a2f062e0af696da4707507c96d3d620cd202","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bd93dbe9c405579747fbe99c6113420dcfcb01","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a75aaaaafea8b6d5ba8a0408cb47a90ffc33df93","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ee3973bf2ed0a4abec12104a2077940e69e122","tid":1487253,"uid":174386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"Push